verses.verse: <S%H1288>Blessed<s%> be the <S%H8034>name<s%> of <S%H3068>Yahweh,<s%> from this time <S%H6258>forth<s%> <S%H5704>and<s%> <S%H5769>forevermore.<s%>

that he may <S%H3427>set<s%> him with <S%H5081>princes,<s%> even with the <S%H5081>princes<s%> of his <S%H5971>people.<s%>
